Title: Requires electronic filing of all lobbying filings
Summary: Requires electronic filing of all lobbying filings with the commission on ethics and lobbying in government.
LawCode: Ren §§1-u & 1-v to be §§1-v & 1-w, add §1-u, Leg L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the legislative law, in relation to requiring electronic filing of all lobbying filings
